name: One-Bedroom-Suite-Queen-
alt: This photo showcases our 600 square foot suite, featuring either a Queen size bed with a sitting bench at the foot of the bed. French doors separate the bedroom and living room. The living room includes a seating area with one armchair, a full size sofa, and ottoman. In the center of the lounge area is a glass coffee table with matching end table with lamp. Adjacent to the seating area is a full size bar with marble counter top and  three bar stools. . Wall decor includes Italian inspired artwork. The bathroom is made with Italian marble and features a 55 gallon soaking tub.
